Description: Secure SQL tool for AI agents to interact with databases
 A Python-based secure SQL tool designed for AI agents to safely interact
 with databases. Features include:
  - Natural language to SQL query translation
  - Safe execution with schema reflection
  - Multi-LLM provider support (Groq, OpenAI, Gemini, DeepSeek)
  - Database independence (PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, OracleDB)
 .
 Licensed under the Apache License 2.0. For commercial licensing options,
 please refer to the upstream project documentation.

